🛠 ATELIER 1 — Initialisation du projet NETOPS-CORP

Outils utilisés : Git, yamllint, ansible-lint, GitLab CI
Objectif : Créer la structure complète du projet et le pipeline CI/CD

*************************************************************************************************************************
Étape 1 — Créer la structure du projet

mkdir netops-corp && cd netops-corp
git init

# Structure professionnelle NetOps
mkdir -p inventories/{production,staging}/{host_vars,group_vars}
mkdir -p inventories/production/group_vars/{all,routers,switches,dc,branches}
mkdir -p playbooks/{deploy,validate,rollback,diagnostics}
mkdir -p roles group_vars/{all,routers,switches,dc,branches,wan}
mkdir -p host_vars templates/{bgp,vlans,acl,ospf,sdwan,aci}
mkdir -p tests/{pre_checks,post_checks,unit,lab}
mkdir -p scripts/{inventory,monitoring,diag,perf,aci,sdwan}
mkdir -p docs backups logs reports

cat > .gitignore << 'EOF'
*.retry
.vault_pass
vault_pass.txt
*.pyc
__pycache__/
.env
generated_configs/
*.log
backups/
EOF

cat > .yamllint.yml << 'EOF'
extends: default
rules:
  line-length:
    max: 120
  truthy:
    allowed-values: ['true', 'false']
  comments:
    min-spaces-from-content: 1
EOF

